<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/landing.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

        <div class="bg-orbs" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, #0f172a 0%, #020617 100%);">
            <div class="orb orb-1"
                style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="container hero">
            <div class="security-status-bar">
                <span class="pulse-dot"
                    style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #10b981; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block;"></span>
                SYSTEMS ONLINE: NEURAL BEHAVIORAL MONITORING V2.4
            </div>

            <h1>Secure Your <br> <span class="gradient-text">Digital Sovereignty</span></h1>

            <p>Aegis Vault is the first Zero-Trust gateway to abandon static credentials for <strong>Continuous
                    Behavioral Authentication</strong>. By mapping your biometric interaction rhythm, we ensure that
                your assets remain yours, even if your keys are stolen.</p>

            <button class="btn" onclick="window.location.href='/auth'">Initialize Vault Access</button>

            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Temporal Profiling</h3>
                    <p>Advanced Keystroke Dynamics analyze the flight and dwell times of your digital pulse. Our engine
                        detects script-based injection in under 50ms.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Spatial Telemetry</h3>
                    <p>Human mouse movement is inherently curved. By detecting robotic linearity and instant cursor
                        "warps," we nullify 99% of remote hijack attempts.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>Route Integrity</h3>
                    <p>Continuous monitoring of session logic. If an API request bypasses the expected behavioral
                        sequence, the session is purged from memory instantly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>